"• Apply: push folder/device limits (copiers, hashers, pullerMaxPendingKiB, scanProgressIntervalS, numConnections) to a running Syncthing instance. For folders on FAT/FUSE filesystems it also sets modTimeWindowS=2, ignorePerms=true, and disables ownership & xattr sync.\n"
